Vinyama vikuruvikuru vingafikako yayi ku virwa ivi chifukwa vili kutali chomene na mtunda.
Kufuma waka apo ŵanthu ŵakambira kukhala mu virwa vya Galapagos, vinyama vinandi vyambaso kukhala mu virwa ivi nga ni mbuzi, mahachi, ng'ombe, mbeŵa, mphaka, na ntcheŵe.
Usange mungaluta ku North panji ku South Pole mu nyengo yakuzizima, mungasanga kuti kwafipa comene, ndipo zuŵa likufuma yayi.
Ivi vikovwira kuti munthu wawone makora maora gha ku mpoto chifukwa mtambo ukufipa chomene.
Pakuti malo agha ghali na ŵanthu ŵachoko chomene, ungweru nawo ukuŵapo yayi, ntheura mungadokera kuwona nyenyezi.
Ŵanthu ku vyaru vya ŵazungu ŵakuwona kuti nchito za ku Japan ni zapachanya kuluska za ku vyaru vinyake.
Ŵakuvwara vyakuvwara vya ku nchito, ndipo ŵakucemana mazina gha ku nchito panji mazina gha mbumba.
Kugwirizana n'kofunika kwambiri pa ntchito, ndipo kuyenera kugogomezera khama la gulu osati kuyamikira kupambana kwa munthu payekha.
Kanandi ŵantchito ŵakwenera kukolerana na ŵabwana ŵawo pa chilichose icho ŵakukhumba kuchita, ndipo ŵakwenera kupulikira ivyo ŵabwana ŵawo ŵakuyowoya.
